# Cross-origin isolation headers for the Playground (deferred).
#
# When the live-wallet Playground lands, restore this block scoped to the route
# it lives on (e.g. /web/playground/*). The two headers together make the page
# cross-origin isolated, which the WASM runtime requires for SharedArrayBuffer
# and OPFS access. Hosts that do not read _headers (e.g. CloudFront) must
# reproduce the same headers in their own CDN/server config.
#
# /web/playground/*
#   Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
#   Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
